{"tid":2218161,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：美國用了龐大的人口令病毒適應人體，變成無礙的風土病，好似香港的沙士一樣。","createTime":"2020-09-26T04:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T11:05:36.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8c6d5833b188292eb4dcd80d5e6fec32e46cb4","tid":2218161,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iMY9KCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMY9KCN.jpg&h=c233332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳雲：美國研究發現，Covid-19在美國有了更強大傳播能力的變種0614G，令到口罩、洗手及人群隔離毫無幫助，但這個變種的殺傷力不會增強。0614G的變種是美國目前大幅度給感染的原因。<br />\n陳雲按：這個報導在挑戰大家的醫學常識。即是說，病毒已經適應人體，變成無礙的風土病，好似香港2003年的沙士一樣，到了第三年就毫無殺傷力。也就是說，美國用了龐大的人口傳播，令新冠病毒變種，變成無礙健康的一般流感病毒。也就是說，愛好自由、隨便逛街玩樂、BLM示威甚至蓄意開感染病毒party的美國人戰勝了新冠病毒。"},{"pid":"42aa0be3789a92d7f1fc7c10a075f50dcdb26700","tid":2218161,"uid":196924,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"沙士無殺傷力...<br />\n叫佢去支那拎支SARS樣本試下"},{"pid":"4b06cacb55ae5bf1ef276e8417ab6bc25bd1efd6","tid":2218161,"uid":21279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"老師又中<br />\n老師好野"},{"pid":"7beb4abb4d5b0b6f634102754e65e0ed743b4a4f","tid":2218161,"uid":137159,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當年沙士撚有係香港大流行過，如果係起碼死幾萬人啦，創造歷史？"},{"pid":"355882e357dda8c3774afc24562cabe256f84cb7","tid":2218161,"uid":157994,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:32:38.000Z","msg":"總之永續基本法work啦"},{"pid":"5d7527b3df38d0a7a3e443d64284f1589e69860f","tid":2218161,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"真乖"},{"pid":"6d6014dab6ea53af5ca08be1bc1e348bc43f87fd","tid":2218161,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f8c6d5833b188292eb4dcd80d5e6fec32e46cb4","tid":2218161,"ui